the representative of Japan, in relation to the statement by the representative of the 
Democratic People&#8217;s Republic of Korea. 
</p>
<p>13. At the same meeting, statements in exercise of a second right of reply were made by 
the representative of the Islamic Republic of Iran, in relation to the statement by the 
representative of Israel; the representative of the Democratic People&#8217;s Republic of Korea, in 
