Human Rights 
</b></p>
<p>62. At the 42nd meeting, on 26 March 2009, the representative of Cuba introduced draft 
resolution A/HRC/10/L.21/Rev.1, sponsored by Cuba and co-sponsored by Algeria, 
Belarus, Bhutan, Bolivia, China, the Democratic People&#8217;s Republic of Korea, Ecuador, 
Egypt (on behalf of the Group of African States), Iran (Islamic Republic of), Nicaragua, the </p>


