</b></p>
<p>Russian Federation, Sri Lanka, the Syrian Arab Republic, Togo, Uruguay, Venezuela 
(Bolivarian Republic of), Viet Nam and Zimbabwe. Subsequently, Angola joined the 
sponsors. 
